data.horoscope_data: Your emotional nature may seem revved up for action today, Leo, although it could be that you don't know what direction to drive in. The engine is running, but for some reason the windshield looks a bit cloudy. Try to key into the areas in your life that need a major overhaul. Look to transform them for the better. Once your windshield is clear, kick your motor into gear and go for it. Initiate the action or else you may find yourself being acted upon.
